<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1328870-does-it-have-an-end-no-this-is-a">Does it have an end? No. This is a reference book. You never finish it, or you start it afresh. The nice thing is that it is not about quotations. It has loose ends. Sometimes you take one side, another time another...</a>
</div>
