<span id="freeTextContainer15312905244361271581">When you read Rumi, a sudden mystical fog wraps you and teleports you to places unknown; places where you long to go. This book gives you the most basic ideas of life with subtle hints and hard hitting thoughts. You might disagree with Rumi on certain points, but never you &apos;ll discard his teachings all together; as his expression is so beautiful that it is impossible not to admire. Indeed, it is &quot;The Essential Rumi&quot;.</span>
  <span id="freeText15312905244361271581" style="display:none">When you read Rumi, a sudden mystical fog wraps you and teleports you to places unknown; places where you long to go. This book gives you the most basic ideas of life with subtle hints and hard hitting thoughts. You might disagree with Rumi on certain points, but never you 'll discard his teachings all together; as his expression is so beautiful that it is impossible not to admire. Indeed, it is "The Essential Rumi".</span>
